abstract: President Trump had a busy morning on Twitter and the radio, in a tirade that rivaled his most grievance-filled moments since becoming president.
snippet: President Trump had a busy morning on Twitter and the radio, in a tirade that rivaled his most grievance-filled moments since becoming president.
lead_paragraph: WASHINGTON — President Trump made a number of staff moves on Thursday to ensure he will be surrounded by a cadre of loyalists at the White House even as he raged against an ever-growing cast of perceived enemies that included his former chief of staff, an impeachment witness, a juror he accused of bias and a Democratic rival.

abstract: The Iraqi government has given NATO the green light to stay in the country, the alliance's chief said Thursday, weeks after Iraq demanded foreign forces leave the country over the U.S. killing of Iran’s top general near the Baghdad airport.
snippet: The Iraqi government has given NATO the green light to stay in the country, the alliance's chief said Thursday, weeks after Iraq demanded foreign forces leave the country over the U.S. killing of Iran’s top general near the Baghdad airport.
lead_paragraph: BRUSSELS — The Iraqi government has given NATO the green light to stay in the country, the alliance's chief said Thursday, weeks after Iraq demanded foreign forces leave the country over the U.S. killing of Iran’s top general near the Baghdad airport.
headline_main: Iraq Green-Lights Resumption of NATO Training Effort
headline_print_headline: Iraq Green-Lights Resumption of NATO Training Effort

abstract: Some Washington hands see Judy Shelton as a dark-horse candidate to become chairwoman — while others think a central bank veteran is still favorite.

abstract: The candidates take a breath, and a top Iowa Democrat resigns. This is your morning tip sheet.
snippet: The candidates take a breath, and a top Iowa Democrat resigns. This is your morning tip sheet.
lead_paragraph: Late at night, journalists gathered at Klobuchar’s “Amy for America” primary night party in Concord, N.H., after her third-place finish in the state.

abstract: A summary decision kicks an untold number of legal immigrants off the path to citizenship.
snippet: A summary decision kicks an untold number of legal immigrants off the path to citizenship.
lead_paragraph: The Freudian concept of psychological projection refers to the behavior of people who, unable to acknowledge their own weaknesses, ascribe those same failings to others. President Trump provides a striking example in his multiple post-impeachment rants calling those who sought his removal “vicious” and “mean.” His choice of the word “mean” caught my attention, because I’ve been thinking for some time now that the United States has become a mean country.
